<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٥٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{آخِذٌ بِنَاصِيَتِهَا}</span> ... مَالِكُهَا، وَالمُتَصَرِّفُ فِيهَا.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(٥٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَيَسْتَخْلِفُ}</span> ... يَاتِي بِقَوْمٍ آخَرِينَ يَخْلُفُونَكُمْ فِي دِيَارِكُمْ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
